Class ReceivedComplexPiece

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jmr.wrapper.common.complex.ReceivedComplexPiece
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<ReceivedComplexPiece>

    public class ReceivedComplexPiece
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<ReceivedComplexPiece>
    Networking Library ReceivedComplexPiece.java Purpose: A piece of a complex object received from a stream. This piece will later be used to form back together the complex object and pass it to the event listener.
    Version:
    1.0 7/25/2014
    Author:
    Jon R (Baseball435)
